{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"65384-omuwala-norah","title":"Omuwala Norah","description":"Norah loves her doll and gets worried one day when she is not able to find it.","language":"Luganda","langCode":"lg","isRtl":false,"level":"4","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Annet  Ssebaggala"],"illustrators":["Melany  Pietersen"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/65384-omuwala-norah"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93398/size3/6e47cce5d03279405b1fe8c71a479888.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93398/size6/6e47cce5d03279405b1fe8c71a479888.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89675/size6/205bb1ba2a88d032555ad6f00785ca94.jpg","text":"Omuwala Norah\nyalina kiddole ngabakiyita Selah.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89676/size6/56377851799f3a1653c2b896e62f9795.jpg","text":"Norah yalinga ayagala nnyo kiddolekye. Yazanyanganakyo era nga alyanakyo emisana. Nekiro nga yebaka nakyo.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89677/size6/2cab924141498c90dc78020895211676.jpg","text":"Olunaku lumu, Norah yanoonya kiddole kye buuli wamu, naye ngatakiraba. Norah yeralikirira nnyo!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89678/size6/d5cd3dabdfa06a9950ce69ab4b024bfa.jpg","text":"Maama we yeyakigyawo nakitwaala nakyooza nga Norah tamanyi. \nMaama yayoza kiddole nakiwanika emanju waggulu kufumbiro kisobole okukala obulungi.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89679/size6/353d2783981288eaed23b62f953d5323.jpg","text":"Naye Norah yali munakuwavu nnyo. Maama we yamugamba, \"Norah teweralikirira, beera mugumu.\"","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89680/size6/6c95c2ea9185b6ac9a73b4dc2606a184.jpg","text":"Mukiseera ekyakawungeezi, Maama yaleeta kiddole nakiwa Norah. Kyali kitukula nnyo nga kiri nga ekipya!","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89681/size6/7ce113f65c2f59a6597d7d79bc5a94e5.jpg","text":"Norah yasanyuka nnyo. Nabuukabuuka! Nazinamu! Nasekannyo!","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/89682/size6/212f2164440a6f06f761176df74daf97.jpg","text":"Yafukamira wansi neyebaza maamawe.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":8,"words":87}}